ge.andP;  The strongest features of the program arethe page design and graphics tools in which it outstrips many dedicatedpublishing packages, and its dynamic data exchange.andM;WordStar will improve this import facility in Legacy before its 1 Marchdelivery date, although Corr insists this will be transparent in the finalproduct.andM;Legacy, which win also be sold in the UK by its original developers NBI, willsport a comparable price to other word processing packages said Corr, andwill probably be around andlsqb;British poundsandrsqb; 400.andO;</TEXT></DOC>